Alan H. Auerbach



Mr. Alan H. Auerbach is Independent Director at Radius Health, Inc. and Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer at Puma Biotechnology, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Radius Health, Inc.
Mr. Auerbach was previously employed as President & Chief Executive Officer by Cougar Biotechnology, Inc., Vice President & Senior Research Analyst by Wells Fargo Securities, Vice President & Research Analyst by Seidler Cos., Inc., Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer by Innovative Acquisitions Corp., and a Principal by Diagnostic Products Corp.
He received his undergraduate degree from Boston University and a graduate degree from the University of Southern California.



