Alan H. Auerbach

Age : 47Public asset : 354,388,471 USDLinked companies :  Puma Biotechnology Inc -  Radius Health Inc 





Summary 



Mr. Alan H. Auerbach is Chairman, President, CEO & Secretary at Puma Biotechnology, Inc.He is on the Board of Directors at Radius Health, Inc. Mr. Auerbach was previously employed as President, Chief Executive Officer & Director by Cougar Biotechnology, Inc. /Old/, Vice President & Senior Research Analyst by Wells Fargo Securities (Old), Vice President & Research Analyst by Seidler Cos., Inc., a Principal by Diagnostic Products Corp., and Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer by Innovative Acquisitions Corp.He received his undergraduate degree from Boston University and a graduate degree from the University of Southern California.



Current positions of Alan H. Auerbach 









